sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant API as Express API
    participant Cache
    participant Replica as MySQL Replica

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
    Note over Client,Replica: First Request - Cache MISS

    Client->>API: GET /api/products/101
    API->>Cache: Check cache key: /api/products/101
    Cache-->>API: MISS (not found)

    Note over API: X-Cache: MISS header

    API->>Replica: SELECT * FROM products WHERE id=101
    Replica-->>API: Product data
    API->>Cache: Store in cache (300s TTL)
    API-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>X-Cache: MISS<br/>{product data}
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
    Note over Client,Replica: Second Request - Cache HIT

    Client->>API: GET /api/products/101
    API->>Cache: Check cache key: /api/products/101
    Cache-->>API: HIT (data found)

    Note over API: X-Cache: HIT header<br/>No database query!

    API-->>Client: 200 OK<br/>X-Cache: HIT<br/>{cached data}
    end
